cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.DL 

This paper deals with the construction of folksonomies, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and social media (cs.SI). The use of metadata and hierarchical relations also falls under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the use of statistics to determine which relations to retain or discard is related to computational complexity (cs.CY) and machine learning (cs.DL).
